Program: Discovery
Title: Electric cars and the car of the future
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxy7
Last Broadcast Date: 08 November 2001
A report on electric cars, could they help solve the energy crisis? The car of the future is likely to be run on electricity. With car makers already able to roll out the technology, it is possible cars that are safer and more intelligent will soon be on our roads.